{"type": "article", "id": 29962, "title": "像窗户一样的壁灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-21T23:01:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 67, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607212141370o8ECJKbRdaz6iyY.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>即便是在没有窗户的房间，你同样能用氛围灯模拟出穿过窗户的阳光了。今天要介绍的这款壁灯 Window 是 Siyu Lou 的设计作品，它不仅可以为无窗的小房间提供温暖的灯光，将数个组合在一起后还能作为装饰使用。壁灯内置了一张能够灵活调节的 LED 灯板，只要轻轻一拉，就会像窗帘一样降下，倾泻出温暖的光芒。在家里挂上这么一张不是用来遮挡光线的“窗帘”，还挺有趣的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721214224AWOYm15GinkUKNbS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721214224bpPKAeBkxhZRlSs9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721214224814MXD2LAyvCpia0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721214224uht85msr9DjgQxCp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}